description:
Lanternium is an adventure puzzle game in which the main character - Raccoon find himself in a magical world. Soon he realized that this world is full of dangers and it's dwellers are in serious trouble...
You have to find out what happened in this fantastic world and help the Raccoon find his way home!

Features:
* Puzzles with colors that can be solved with the magic lantern;
* 3 fabulous locations containing;
* 60 game levels with a unique style and different mechanics;
* Free mode with new levels;
* Hardcore mode for the players who are ready for the most difficult challenges.

Rayflector is a bite-sized game about using the mirrors and other to direct a stream of particles to the receptacles. Game elements:
- Mirrors change the particle angle either by +90 or -90 degrees;
- Walls destroy particles if they touch them;
- Repeaters boost the particles power, or else they will disappear after losing all of their energy;
- Splitters divert the particles stream to 2 different sides;
- Receptacles also destroy the particles, but it counts as a game objective.
